snippet.title: BABYLON’S FALL – E3 2018 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: BABYLON’S FALL is a brand-new, ground breaking project being developed in partnership with PlatinumGames Inc. It will release on the PlayStation®4 computer entertainment system and STEAM® in 2019.
